line_1: To drink the young couple good luck,
line_2: Frae punch-bowl as big as Dumbuck.

line_1: By Method, rather than by Luck;
line_2: But granting Matters should be spoke

line_1: I'd not be Mævius to have Maevius' Luck.
line_2: But let him conquer e'er one Blow be struck;

line_1: Who while he peep'd into the Bath had the Luck
line_2: To find himself suddenly chang'd to a Buck.
